---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — Patriotometer" description="Patriotometer privacy policy. We don't collect any data.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">&larr; Back to quiz</a>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-6 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 leading-relaxed">
      <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> February 23, 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">The short version</h2>

      <p>
        We don't collect any data. The quiz runs entirely in your browser. Your answers are never
        transmitted anywhere.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">What we don't collect</h2>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Quiz answers or results</li>
        <li>Personal information of any kind</li>
        <li>Cookies (we don't use them)</li>
        <li>Analytics data about your quiz responses</li>
        <li>IP addresses for tracking purposes</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">How the quiz works</h2>

      <p>
        All quiz logic runs client-side in your web browser using JavaScript. Your answers are stored
        temporarily in browser memory while you take the quiz. When you close the tab or refresh the
        page, everything is gone.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">Image generation</h2>

      <p>
        The shareable meme image is generated locally in your browser using the Canvas API. The image
        is created on your device and downloaded directly to your computer. No image data is sent to
        any server.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">Third-party services</h2>

      <p>
        This site is hosted on Netlify. Netlify may collect standard web server logs (IP address,
        browser type, pages visited) as part of their hosting service. We do not access or use this
        data. See <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" class="underline" style="color: var(--color-accent);" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Netlify's privacy policy</a> for details.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8">Contact</h2>

      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Reach out via
        <a href="https://centricle.com/contact/" class="underline" style="color: var(--color-accent);">centricle.com/contact</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
